description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Registered Nurse – Dementia/Mental Health/Neurological Conditions (RMN, RNLD, RGN) &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Rated Overall Outstanding by CQC (January 2020) - New Unit opening soon&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Applications from Preceptorship Nurses are welcome &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Moston Grange is looking for nurses who are motivated to provide and coordinate care that is safe, compassionate, evidence-based and person-centred. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Nurses who join our successful team will be supported to provide leadership by acting as a role model for best practice in the delivery of human rights based approaches and play an active and equal role in the interdisciplinary team, collaborating with a range of colleagues. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Moston Grange will provide excellent clinical and managerial support for nurses and facilitate learning and continuous professional development for this multi-faceted role:-&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Managing complex health issues&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Day- to-day operational management&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Leadership responsibility for a team of staff&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Working with systems to provide integrated care&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;What can we offer:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Comprehensive induction and commitment to ongoing training&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Professional development (including support with revalidation)&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A competitive salary&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Paid breaks&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;£500 bonus on completion of 6 month probationary process&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;£1,000 bonus on completion of 2 years’ service&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enhanced over-time rate&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Enhanced disclosure cost coverage&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Cost coverage of NMC Registration fees&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;We look forward to hearing from you. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span&gt;Please contact Lucy or Jack for an informal discussion about the role and opportunities on 0161219 1300&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;Equilibrium Healthcare is an equal opportunities employer. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span&gt;The role is subject to proof of eligibility to work in the UK, an enhanced Disclosure and Barring Service Check and satisfactory references. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
